вҚқ monadic, B is 0 0 ----------------------------------

      )ERASE FN
вҲҮFN
 вҺ•ES 0 0              вҚқ Resets вҺ•EM and вҺ•ET
 вҺ•ET                  вҚқ print event type:            0 0

 '2+3' вҺ•EA 'AвҶҗB)вҶҗ2)'  вҚқ Causes a syntax error, print 5
 вҺ•ET                  вҚқ print event type:            2 2

 вҺ•ES 0 0              вҚқ Resets вҺ•EM and вҺ•ET
 вҺ•ET                  вҚқ print event type:            0 0
вҲҮ

      )CHECK
OK      - no stale functions
OK      - no stale values
OK      - no stale indices
OK      - no duplicate parents


      FN
0 0
5
2 2
0 0


